    <remarks>
      <format type="text/markdown"><![CDATA[  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="74bd2-102">這個類別用做為一部分<xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.ColorKeyFrameCollection>搭配<xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.ColorAnimationUsingKeyFrames>以動畫方式顯示<xref:System.Windows.Media.Color>沿著一組主要畫面格的屬性值。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="74bd2-102">This class is used as part of a <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.ColorKeyFrameCollection> in conjunction with a <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.ColorAnimationUsingKeyFrames> to animate a <xref:System.Windows.Media.Color> property value along a set of key frames.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="74bd2-103">主要畫面格定義的區段<xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.ColorAnimationUsingKeyFrames>其所屬。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="74bd2-103">A key frame defines a segment of the <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.ColorAnimationUsingKeyFrames> to which it belongs.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="74bd2-104">每個主要畫面格有 target<xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.ColorKeyFrame.Value%2A>和<xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.ColorKeyFrame.KeyTime%2A>。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="74bd2-104">Each key frame has a target <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.ColorKeyFrame.Value%2A> and a <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.ColorKeyFrame.KeyTime%2A>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="74bd2-105"><xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.ColorKeyFrame.KeyTime%2A>指定的時間主要畫面格之<xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.ColorKeyFrame.Value%2A>應該達到。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="74bd2-105">The <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.ColorKeyFrame.KeyTime%2A> specifies the time at which the key frame's <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.ColorKeyFrame.Value%2A> should be reached.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="74bd2-106">主要畫面格以動畫顯示從上一個主要畫面格的目標值至它自己的目標值。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="74bd2-106">A key frame animates from the target value of the previous key frame to its own target value.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="74bd2-107">先前的主要畫面格結束，並在達到它自己的索引鍵時間時結束時啟動它。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="74bd2-107">It starts when the previous key frame ends and ends when its own key time is reached.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="74bd2-108">獨立的主要畫面格喜歡<xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.DiscreteColorKeyFrame>建立突然"跳躍點 」 值 （沒有插補） 之間。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="74bd2-108">Discrete key frames like <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.DiscreteColorKeyFrame> create sudden "jumps" between values (no Interpolation).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="74bd2-109">換句話說，動畫的屬性不會一直主要畫面格的索引鍵時間的時間點動畫的屬性會突然跳到目標值變更。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="74bd2-109">In other words, the animated property does not change until the key frame's key time is reached at which point the animated property goes suddenly to the target value.</span></span>  
  
 ]]></format>
